@startuml fig-quic-vs-tcp
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 10
skinparam shadowing false
title QUIC vs TCP+TLS

package "TCP + TLS" as tcptls #E3F2FD {
    card "Handshake TCP\n1 RTT" as tcp_hs #BBDEFB
    card "Handshake TLS\n1-2 RTT" as tls_hs #BBDEFB
    card "Total: 2-3 RTT" as tcp_tot #FFCDD2
}

package "QUIC (HTTP/3)" as quic #E8F5E9 {
    card "Handshake QUIC\n1 RTT sau 0-RTT" as q_hs #C8E6C9
    card "Total: 1 sau 0 RTT" as q_tot #C8E6C9
}

legend bottom
TCP: straturi separate, blocare HOL
QUIC: criptare integrata, fara blocare HOL
QUIC: migrare conexiune (schimbare IP OK)
QUIC: bazat UDP, in userspace
Folosit de HTTP/3, servicii Google
endlegend
@enduml
